Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: White Christmas in Vermont
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bwfv
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Jan 1979
Christmas holiday in Vermont, the state which knows how to cope with snow. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less